headline: The Top 5 Analyst Questions From Jabil’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Jabil’s fourth quarter delivered results that met Wall Street’s expectations, with strength attributed to robust demand in its Intelligent Infrastructure segment and steady contributions from Regulated Industries and Connected Living and Digital Commerce.
